&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.thatsoftwareguy.com/scr_article/pricing_dollars.png"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Displaying the discount as a dollar figure off the base price&lt;/td&gt;
