&lt;li&gt;100GB Website Traffic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;100 Email Address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On top of this, Pinnacle Cart offers two additional Enterprise Level Solutions aimed at high-volume-traffic stores that require a lot of server resources. These two packages solutions are; VPS1 ($249/month) and VPS2 ($349/month)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Ease-to-Use&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As stated at the beginning, Pinnacle Cart offers a comprehensive, easy to use control panel, easy tools to customize your website design and it's scalable to any size, from startups to large enterprises. The system is built fairly simple that it accommodate both novice and advanced users. You can simply edit your website design with HTML/CSS built-in editor. In the store setting, you can easily setup things like payments, shipping, tax options, currencies and languages.&lt;/p&gt;
 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pinnacle Cart offers a reasonable range of built-in features to run an eCommerce business. The platform allows you to add an unlimited number of products on all plans, manage your product, inventory tracking and order tracking functionalities. They also provide  up to 30 responsive templates that a fully customizable your individual needs.
When it comes to payment gateways options Pinnacle Cart supports the most widely used payment methods - with 30 different options and 7 real-time shipping quote that include USPS, FedEx, UPS, VIPparcel, Canada Post, Stamps.com and Endicia.
Their SEO Capabilities allow you to customize SEO on the product page, custom URLs, meta titles and meta descriptions for your products.
Some other noticeable features include automatic tax calculation with Avalara Ava Tax or Exact-o-Tax, multi-languages, different currency display, one-page check that includes guest checkout, autoresponders emails, bulk import/export and discount &amp; gift certificates.&lt;/p&gt;
 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Customer support&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pinnacle Cart offers phone support, but of course limited to working hours (Mon-Fri 6am-7pm PST; Sat 9am-6pm PST) on all plans and also offer email support and online chat. They also have to use resources such as video tutorials, developer community, knowledge base, user forum, blog, YouTube, Facebook, and Twitter.&lt;/p&gt;
 
&lt;p&gt;In conclusion, Pinnacle Cart is an all-in-one eCommerce solution that is competing among the big names in the industry such as BigCommerce and WordPress. It should be noted that every eCommerce platform does have pros and cons and Pinnacle Cart is not an immune to that. They offer a 14-days free trial without any commitment, and it's in your best interest to utilize this offer to the fullest before committing. The best way to choose a platform is through "Trial n Error". &lt;/p&gt;</description><link>http://www.ecommercespot.com/articles/Pinnacle-Cart-Reviews.aspx</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Sep 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Fortune3 Review</title><description>&lt;p&gt;Fortune3 is an all-in-one eCommerce builder and shopping cart software that offer the best solutions to sell your products online. The platform has been in the industry for over a decade now, providing eCommerce service to major popular brands in the market. Fortune3 is web hosted shopping cart that is fully customizable to your individual need.
This shopping cart provides a robust feature and functionality that is packed with thousands of features and tools that makes creating, designing, and managing an online business easy and painless. With Fortune3 you can be able to manage your store online or download the software which allows you to make changes offline and save them for upload.
In this review summary of Fortune3, we are going to discuss key factor that helps to determine if this shopping cart is the right platform for your business.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Fortune3 Pricing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If the cost of the platform is what drives your choice, then you be pleased to know that Fortune3 is the most cost worthy effective platforms. They offer 6 affordable plans for their platform and all include unlimited features, unlimited bandwidth, unlimited email accounts and an unlimited admin accounts unlimited storage and no transaction fees. The payment plans are as follows:
&lt;p&gt;1.Starter Plan $9.95 with a limited of 20 products and zero setup fees&lt;/br&gt;
2.Basic Plan $24.95 with a limit of 50 products and zero setup fees.&lt;/br&gt;
3.Silver Plan $39.95 with a limit of 250 products and zero setup fees.&lt;/br&gt;
4.Gold Plan $69.95 with a limit of 1000 products and zero setup fees.&lt;/br&gt;
5.Platinum $99.95 with a limit of 10000 products and $50 setup fees.&lt;/br&gt;
6.Unlimited Plan $159.95 with unlimited products and $50 setup fees.&lt;/br&gt;
&lt;/br&gt;
It should be noted, that zero transaction fees apply only when you use the Fortune3 credit card services and if you plan on using an external payment processor, all plans excluding the Unlimited Plan will include a 1% transaction fee.
As you can see Fortune has an accommodating plan that fits for all business types, from a small startup to large enterprises. They also offer a 30-day free trial, which stands out from all the competitors.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Fortune3 Ease of Use&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Setting up an eCommerce website through their website is pretty simple which is supported by customizable templates and drag and drop features on tap. On the top menu you will find the setup wizard that guides you to setup the most important information about your online store which includes The admin panel is clean and clear with all the settings tools display visible and user-friendly to both novice and advanced users.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Fortune3 Web Designs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The purpose of having an appealing online store is to stand out of the crowd, Fortune3 offers all the resource your business needs to be unique. They have over 400+ free templates and if these do not meet your needs, then premium templates are available for sale. Their HTML editor is easy to use, so no HTML knowledge is necessary. Another noticeable advantage for Fortune3 - they allow full access to the design and web page source codes this enables you to tweak your website designs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Fortune3 Security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The security of your website and customer data is an important aspect of owning an online business. If you are hosting your website with Fortune3, you do not need to worry about anything. Fortune3 security measure includes McAfee secure, PCI-compliant, 24/7 site monitoring and secure 256-bit SSL certificate that ensures an encrypted checkout experience. You can also upgrade and use your own domain of which Fortune3 offers Geo Trust SSL certificate with 3  different tiers of security; Geo Trust Quick $119/year; Geo Trust Quick SSL Premium $149.00/year with Seal; and Geo Trust True Business ID with EV $299.00/year&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;
 
&lt;h3&gt;Fortune3 Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fortune3 is a rich-feature shopping cart with everything you need to operate an online store. They offer over 1000 features to effectively build, manage and market your online website. These features include an easy product setup to add, edit, import and easily make bulk changes; multiple currencies, up-selling and cross-selling, promo codes, customer reviews and SEO meta tags.
Fortune offers attractive integration tools which include: over 50+ payment processors such as PayPal, Google Wallet, Amazon Payments, Authorize.net, sage pay, etc.; major shipping method integration with real-time rate with FedEx, UPS, USPS, DHL, Canada Post, etc., with one-click printing of your shipping labels directly from the Admin site; Accounting software integration that include QuickBooks, Peachtree, and other popular accounting software.
They also include built-in automatic SEO and Marketing tools that help with the ranking of your store. You can manually and automatically create meta keywords, titles, discretions, Google XML sitemap generator, static HTML pages, etc. Fortune offers automated affiliate programs, social shopping cart-Facebook, advanced mailing list and newsletter. All this gives you the ability to promote your store and ranking.
A notice attractive feature you will be excited about Fortunre3 is their Mobile App which is available on all mobile devices (iOS, Android, and Windows).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;
 
&lt;h3&gt;Fortune3 Customer Support&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fortune offers 24/7 unlimited email and online tech support. Their phone and live support are available between 9am EST to 11:59pm. Besides this, you have access help with the knowledge base, browse help manuals, submit tickets, watch training videos, read FAQs, and online forum. You can also contact them through Facebook and Twitter.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;
 
&lt;h3&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fortune3 offers an eCommerce solution to those who want to set up an online store easily and not hassle with complicated procedures. There are several key aspects to note about Fortune3 like their long 30-days free trial, social media features, marketing tools, and mobile integration.
I would suggest Fortune3 to a business that does not want to worry about website security and those that want to set up their online stores on the least time frame with a tight budget point.&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>http://www.ecommercespot.com/articles/Fortune3-Review.aspx</link><pubDate>Sun, 02 Oct 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>OpenCart Review</title><description>&lt;p&gt;Are you new to the eCommerce market and thinking about opening an online store, then OpenCart eCommerce platform is a good solution to start selling online.
OpenCart is an open-source free to download shopping cart based on PHP/MySQL code, build to be affordable, user-friendly and feature-rich eCommerce solution. OpenCart is a good eCommerce solution for the business owners who are just starting out, because of its low cost and easy to use functionality. Overall, OpenCart is ideal for small to a medium eCommerce store. Since its an open source platform, the only things you need to worry about is hosting and security.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;OpenCart Pricing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OpenCart is completely free to download on their website and there are no hidden costs. The only cost you must be prepared for being for security and hosting fees. In order to enable a wider functionality, you might like to download and install a number of extensions and modules, that comes with their own cost.
However, Opencart offers a free demo testing environment that includes a sample data for a storefront and for the admin backend.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;OpenCart Ease-to-Use&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OpenCart offers a friendly admin panel that is well organized and easy to navigate daily tasks. OpenCart offers tons of free templates that are responsive and can be fully customized to create your own unique store as per an individual need.  I would, however, suggest getting a developer to do this as it can be a tricky process.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/br&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;OpenCart Features&lt;/h3&gt;
